sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Model Registry Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant NotebookPod as Notebook Pod
    participant OSRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MRService as Model Registry Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL Database<br/>5432/TCP TLS1.2+ (optional)

    %% Flow 3: ModelRegistry CR Creation
    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 1: ModelRegistry CR Creation & Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: POST ModelRegistry CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event: ModelRegistry Created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services (HTTP/gRPC/OAuth)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources Created
    Note over MRService: Model Registry Pod Starts
    MRService->>PostgreSQL: Initialize Database Schema<br/>Auth: Password, TLS (optional)
    PostgreSQL-->>MRService: Schema Initialized

    %% Flow 1: Model Registration from Notebook
    Note over NotebookPod,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: Model Registration from Notebook
    NotebookPod->>OAuthProxy: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate Token
    OAuthProxy->>MRService: Forward Request (validated)<br/>HTTP/8080
    MRService->>PostgreSQL: INSERT model metadata<br/>Auth: Password, TLS (optional)
    PostgreSQL-->>MRService: Metadata Stored
    MRService-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP 201 Created
    OAuthProxy-->>NotebookPod: HTTPS Response<br/>Model Registered

    %% Flow 2: Model Query from Dashboard
    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 3: Model Query from Dashboard
    User->>OSRoute: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Session Cookie
    OSRoute->>OAuthProxy: Forward HTTPS Request<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>MRService: Forward Query<br/>HTTP/8080
    MRService->>PostgreSQL: SELECT model metadata<br/>Auth: Password, TLS (optional)
    PostgreSQL-->>MRService: Query Results
    MRService-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP 200 OK + JSON
    OAuthProxy-->>OSRoute: HTTPS Response
    OSRoute-->>User: Model List Displayed
